97
00:08:39,390 --> 00:08:43,520
LUFFY-NO-UMI - SUMO-WANNABE PIRATE RECORD: UNFEATED VS. USOPP

98
00:08:52,840 --> 00:08:54,840
අපි සුමෝ තරඟයක් ගමු!

99
00:09:05,770 --> 00:09:08,600
සූදානම්...

100
00:09:12,230 --> 00:09:14,190
ගෙනයන්න...

101
00:09:14,490 --> 00:09:16,740
